videos.description: Will Wade says the Tigers making the SEC Tournament finals for the first time since 1993 is big, but there is one more step.
videos.headline: Wade discusses magnitude of LSU's championship berth

videos.description: The Tigers' Cameron Thomas says he's looking forward to facing the Crimson Tide in the SEC title tilt.
videos.headline: LSU's Thomas expects 'great game' vs. Alabama
